OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FTurning
OL,6,Fcloudier this evening and overnight
OL,7,Fwith a few spots of rain, more so by
OL,8,Fdawn. Winds staying light and
OL,9,Ftemperatures holding up above
OL,10,Ffreezing. Some fog patches forming
OL,11,Fwhere any clear skies hold on in the
OL,12,Fsouth and east.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FA cloudier day compared to
OL,15,FThursday with outbreaks of rain
OL,16,Fdeveloping on and off through the
OL,17,Fmorning and afternoon, most of which
OL,18,Fwill be light. Feeling colder, though
OL,19,Flight winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
